eet&#8217;s advantage is in the simplicity. &#8220;Most people design this =
product for experts,&#8221; Abouzeid said, &#8220;We design ours for beginn=
ers - we&#8217;re easy, trustworthy, we do it right, and won't take up your=
 whole afternoon.&#8221;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Part of the reason MainStreet ca=
n be so seamless is its laser focus. Today, MainStreet mainly handles feder=
al R&amp;D credits. On average, <strong>MainStreet finds its customers $51k=
 in federal R&amp;D credits twenty minutes</strong>.&nbsp;</p><div class=3D=
